{"tid":1161830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲屋企夏天唔係長開冷氣？","createTime":"2019-05-19T12:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T13:20:02.000Z","uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1c0edd4c8889debcc4b27062a1e112c4025538f4","tid":1161830,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:36:38.000Z","msg":"我屋企不嬲天氣一熱就會長開冷氣<br />\n全家出去一段長時間先會熄<br />\n出去一陣都會照開住慳電啲<br />\n<br />\n但今日出街同啲fd食飯講起佢地好驚訝話冇人會咁開法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話通常好熱先會食飯個時開一陣<br />\n好多時都係訓教先會開 有時唔算太熱仲會定時幾個鐘自動熄<br />\n我就話咁返到去咪好撚熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正常唔係家家戶戶夏天都長開咩?即係平時有係廳就開廳個部<br />\n到訓教或者入房就開房個部咁？佢地就話癡撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我想知到底正常應該係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JoPajmp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJoPajmp.png&h=f8b6eee9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"94dfd38b81b933c59f881db2be5772afeeb97b33","tid":1161830,"uid":21432,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:48:38.000Z","msg":"屌你理得人，電費你自己交鍾意一日開30個鐘關人隱事咩"},{"pid":"f873acb12f7f3f50485920bf4f4713cc39fc62c7","tid":1161830,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:20:02.000Z","msg":"有錢交電費咪得囉. 使乜理人."}]}